<Rzhev41HRuDb> <Our soldiers fought hard battles at Voloklansk and Naro-Fominsk which delayed the enemy for long enough that winter set in and his armoured troops became immobilised in the snow. More reinforcements are arriving and in the new year we are to take the offensive to push the enemy out of his advanced positions near Moscow.>
