<Kerch42DeBr> <The Soviet offensives of the winter have begun to fade out into a series of smaller attacks that can easily be contained.  Our strategic objective for the year is the occupation of the Caucasus with its oil reserves.  Operation Trappenjagd is a preliminary offensive to reconquer the territory lost in the Kerch peninsula as both a prelude to our capture of Sevastopol and to acquire a base from which to begin the invasion of the Kuban.  Luftflotte 4 has been attached to this offensive with the objective of securing overwhelming air superiority.  Our staffeln have been reinforced, and the new Hs129 ground-attack aircraft is to be deployed against Soviet tanks.>
